(Mohoapoani); NRM 569873 [7263], an adult female collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F77CB13DB281FD70364C41EB" box="[964,1141,655,681]" pageId="9" pageNumber="530" value="1844-03-27">
<collectingDate id="EFD7842EF77CB13DB281FD70364C41EB" box="[964,1141,655,681]" pageId="9" pageNumber="530" value="1844-03-27">27 March 1844</collectingDate>
</date>
near 
<location id="8EF20DDDF77CB13DB5FDFD70370A41EB" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:0384EA10F77CB13DB1D2FEB436B4464F:8EF20DDDF77CB13DB5FDFD70370A41EB" box="[1208,1331,655,681]" county="Apies River" municipality="Tswaing" name="Saulspoort" pageId="9" pageNumber="530" stateProvince="Berlin">Saulspoort</location>
; RMNH. 
<taxonomicName id="4C2D2085F77CB13DB1D2FD4C32D9418F" box="[151,224,691,717]" class="Aves" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="9" pageNumber="530" phylum="Chordata" rank="class">AVES</taxonomicName>
.197484 [7261], a female collected 11 (February?) 1842 near 
<location id="8EF20DDDF77CB13DB2E3FD4C3608418F" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:0384EA10F77CB13DB1D2FEB436B4464F:8EF20DDDF77CB13DB2E3FD4C3608418F" box="[934,1073,691,717]" county="Apies River" municipality="Tswaing" name="Apies River" pageId="9" pageNumber="530" stateProvince="Berlin">Apies River</location>
